<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Subscription Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🎉 New Subscription Created</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello Admin,</p>
        
        <p>A new subscription has been created for your platform.</p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>Customer Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{customerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{customerEmail}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <h3>Subscription Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Plan:</strong> {{planName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}} {{amount}}</p>
            <p><strong>Billing Cycle:</strong> {{billingCycle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Next Billing Date:</strong> {{nextBillingDate}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>This subscription has been automatically processed and the customer has been notified.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>Qurieus Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{footerText}}</p>
        <p>{{footerLink}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 